description: The battle fought in two time-periods comes to a climactic conclusion! The X-Men are the only thing that stand between the Evolutionaries and the complete annihilation of the human race. On top of that, learn secrets of Emma Frost’s past and what she had to do with the original Brotherhood of Evil Mutants.
name: First To Last Part 5

description:
FLASH QUESTION: Trapped behind enemy lines, will the Grayson family be able to help the Resistance, or is this their final performance?

A savage attack by the Amazons ends in Dick Grayson’s orphanhood. With Deadman now being the closest thing he has to a family, Dick will have to convince his friend to join him in the Resistance after a vigilante named Vertigo enlists their help. But why was the Graysons’ circus a target of an Amazonian attack? What do they have in their possession that’s worth so much and to what lengths will the Amazons go to attain it?
name: All Eyes on the Prize

has_staff_review.name: Flashpoint: Deadman and the Flying Graysons #2

volume.name: Flashpoint: Deadman and the Flying Graysons

description:
FLASH QUESTION: How many must die to avenge Queen Hippolyta's death and satiate Diana's fury? 
 
There was once a time when Aquaman and Wonder Woman were to be married. For political reasons, it made perfect sense: with their powers combined, together they could conquer the world. But when Diana’s mother was killed by an Atlantean, Wonder Woman and Aquaman’s alliance was broken and the two became mortal enemies.
name: Part Two: The Sacrifice

volume.name: Flashpoint: Wonder Woman and the Furies

description: From a laboratory of the Biofarm pharmaceutical company a deadly virus is stolen. Nathan Never and Branko are instructed to retrieve the bacteriological weapon. Following the tracks of the criminals who carried out the theft leads to the Eurasian continent. Here, on the eve of an important election campaign, subversives are planning an attack on a large scale: they will release the stolen virus in the air, spreading a terrible epidemic. The Alfa agents must try the impossible, moving cautiously and trying not to get caught in a deadly spy network!
name: Missione in Eurasia

description:
FLASH QUESTION: In a world where everyone hates The Outsider, who wants him dead? Will the ruler of Kahndaq have what it takes to finish the job? 
 
Michael Desai is as ruthless in his personal life as he is in the business world. A look back into his origins shows how he took over the crime scene in India and set up the power base he has today. But when Teth-Adam launches an attack to get rid of him, Michael will have to eliminate his nemesis. Can The Outsider’s powers overrule Shazam’s? And even if he does win his battle, will it truly be over?
name: Once Upon a Time in the East

description:
Agguato nella giungla 
May faces a perilous mission into the jungle on the border of the Territories in the South to come to the aid of Major Joanna Gleason , an old childhood friend , in a bid to thwart illicit trafficking of military biotechnology conducted by Lt. Enrique Nagra, the fascinating first love of the Alfa agent.

La casa sulla collina 
The young Kay and his friends decide to improvise investigators to unravel the mystery of an abandoned house, where, long ago, the murder of the father of their classmate has been consumed, and that has now become the basis of a band of Novocain dealers .

I soldati d'acciaio 
Branko and May should keep up with a real army of deadly robots stolen by some military facility and now serving Tarek Douglas III , dangerous international terrorist.

Big red
May is  called to investigate the theft of a giant vegetable from the estate owned by the noble Lord Chester Whoodhouse and his wacky family, a few days after the race that takes place at the annual Springfield fair .
name: Agguato nella giungla

description:
FLASH QUESTION: The villains have mounted a prison break! Now, one lone hero stands in the way. Will Animal Man be able to stop them, or will they have their revenge against Cyborg?

When Cyborg locked Mick Rory away in the Hall of Doom for murdering Firestorm, little did he know the risk that comes from being the target of Heatwave’s vengeance. With help from Eel, a.k.a Plastic Man, Heatwave generates an escape plan. But in order to be successful and gain back the weapons that fuel him, he must get past Atomic Skull and the Meta Gang, Animal Man, and Atom to name a few. And when his monstrous plan for revenge is ultimately revealed, Cyborg will have to worry about saving much more than just himself.
name: Fired Up!

description: Ines is a young woman, who in the past was tied to famous writers, all eventually mysteriously died. What is her true relationship with them ? Nathan and Branko are on her trail , in an adventure spotted with many stories inspired or told by Ines herself , and moving up to an end ... that will br nothing but the beginning of yet another story to tell.
name: Calliope

description: Power Girl is in the big leagues now – and the First Annual "Power Girl Convention" has asked her to attend! But is she ready to meet her #1 fan? How about when that fan decides to keep P.G. around as her best friend and personal bodyguard – forever?
name: Girl Power

description: Dejah Thoris has proclaimed her love for John Carter, but the despicable Warlord of Zodanga has forced her to promise she will marry the Zondangan prince. A Martian woman may not back out of such a pledge, and she may not marry her husband-to-be's killer. John Carter will need an army to change things now. If he can help Tars Tarkas seize control of the Tharks, he might have just that -- but Zodanga's not going down without a fight!

Eclipso is triumphant! He has defeated the world's greatest heroes, destroyed the moon and spit in the face of the greatest forces in the universe. But one JLAer still stands. Can she make things right?
name: Eclipso Rising, Part Six

description: The turbulent past of Legs is finally revealed: the Training Academy , the marriage with Oliver Lawrence, the accuse of murdering her husband, the time spent in jail, the Alfa Agency.
name: La regina bianca

description: Investigating two mysterious deaths linked to a strange machine that gives life to one's favorite novels, Legs finds herself in the tale of "Alice in Wonderland", where, however, something goes wrong: the white rabbit is kidnapped and Legs finds a talking hedgehog as an aide...
name: Nel paese delle meraviglie

description: This is the X-men comic that will have people talking for years! Some candles burn twice as bright and half as long. Some candles don't get a chance to burn at all. Generation Hope discover what happens when a light goes out.
name: Better

description:
FEAR ITSELF TIE-IN!

The X-Men are used to being feared. When FEAR ITSELF finally reaches the west coast, they're going to become well acquainted with the emotion first hand. The unstoppable power of an old foe renewed is heading their way, and they have all the time in the world to realize how little they can do to stop him. And even more time to think about exactly how he's going to destroy San Francisco and everything it stands for.

The origin of The Christian Knight is revealed in this action packed and thought-provoking collection.

Who is the Christian Knight? As danger looms and the Hordes of Hell and other enemies attack, this character steps forth to battle them all in the name of God. But who is the person (or could be persons?) behind the mask?

Published by The Christian Knight Comics Group.
name: The Origin of The Christian Knight

volume.name: The Power of The Christian Knight

description: Tracking a weapon dealer, Legs finds herself in the middle of a civil war, among spies and fighter planes
name: Le aquile di Kane

description: The ancient immortal hero Gilgamesh embodies temporarily in the body of Legs. But the hero is tired , the only thing he wants is to die ....
name: L'immortale

description: May sees something strange in Legs behavior, and, with the help of Sigmund and Harvey, began the investigation which lead her to discover the origin of the Black Dames.
name: Dietro la maschera

description: Legs and May are thrown into a sort of "amusement park" which reconstructs the complicated world of the "Orlando Furioso" created by medieval writer Ludovico Ariosto. Here they will face wizards and warriors, discovering in the end that it was a trick adopted by the Sin Club to keep them out of the Agency, where is hidden a chip needed to establish their new, criminal plan.
name: La Legs Furiosa

description:
Continued from Titans Annual #1

"The Methuselah Imperative" continues! From the ashes of defeat comes the secret of life itself as Deathstroke's master plan reaches its stunning conclusion. Plus, this is it: Arsenal leads a Titans mutiny – but who will survive? Guest-starring The Mad Hatter, Dr. Sivana and Dr. Impossible!
name: The Methuselah Imperative, Part 2 of 3

description: Death finally claims one of the T.H.U.N.D.E.R. Agents! Dark secrets about the history of T.H.U.N.D.E.R. surface as the Iron Maiden continues her assault on the team. Featuring guest art from Mike Grell and Nick Dragotta!
name: Yours Always; A Farewell To Our Hero

description: It is a welcome home party for Ebony White after being away at Mr. Carter's School for three weeks.
name: Welcome Home, Ebony!
The Return of the S.S. Raven
Army Operas No. 2: Pvt. O'Toole aka Pvt O'Toole
Pool's Toadstool Facial Cream aka Love Comes to The Spirit
The Biography of a Big Shot: Joe Frisk

description:
The dark and foggy, "New London", the city of steam, is the scene of fervent preparations: the plan of George Gordon Byron, Lord of the city is finally coming true. Soon, the "Skyrumble", a military satellite that can block for a long period of time any electronic device, will be in his hands and he will be able to push back Earth in a restored Victorian. But Legs and Janet Blaise, chasing a group of ruthless criminals who call themselves the "Amazon", will interfere with his plans.
A steampunk style adventure for Legs Weaver.
name: Nuova Londra

description: “The Agency” has to   face a woman who can control swarms of killer bees , and in the process of implementing a deadly revenge.
name: Api assassine
The Last Gang in Rotten Row
Policewoman Ellen aka Dressed To Kill

description:
The origin of Mr. Christian is revealed in this action packed and thought-provoking collection.

Beginning with a childhood dream that occurs in 1939 and into the Origin of Mr. Christian, Christian Superheroes: Mr. Christian is 20 pages w/full color cover and b/w interior art. Published by The Christian Knight Comics Group.
name: The Origin of Mr. Christian
